title: Fix travis ci tests
body:
I was looking into why Travis CI fails and there are some things that need to be fixed. Maybe someone has some ideas. I fixed the jQuery, Cheerio, Logg, Modernizr, MsNodeSql, Node_Redis, PouchDB, Restify, Scroller
_EDIT 1:_ Also fixed Sugar, Backgrid, jQueryUI
## Syntax checking:

ExtJS: 
- bool should be changed to boolean
- a lot of "Overloads cannot differ only by return type" errors
- some "cannot extend interface....types are incompatible" errors

Intl:
- I think this extension should be removed because Intl is defined in lib.d.ts already

Sencha_Touch: 
- same as ExtJS

Sugar:
- some strange stack overflow error (could be a bug in tsc)
## Typing tests:

Backgrid:
- needs "--target ES5" compiler parameter

Ember:
- lots of errors

Intl:
- I think this extension should be removed because Intl is defined in lib.d.ts already

jQueryUI:
- compile error in lines 1092 and 1140 caused by https://typescript.codeplex.com/workitem/1522

jsDeferred:
- lots of errors

SammyJS:
- lots of errors

Sencha_Touch:
- lots of errors related to type definition errors

ThreeJS:
- using some webkit... and moz... properties resulting in lots of "property ... does not exist on value of type"

versions. Otherwise, the standard promise unwrapping behaviour does not
type check correctly.

title: Fix, optimizations and new functionnalities for knockout definition
body:
Hi, 

This new version of the definition of Knockout offer some usefull functionnalities :
- inheritance of observable and computed
- inheritance of template sources
- inheritance of template engines
- append missing types
- append types in all methods
- Fix issues and optimize code
#### Here is the details of the pull request :

Append KnockoutSubscription and KnockoutSubscribable
Make observable, computed and observable array inherits from subscribable
Append properties in interfaces when necessary

Append missing properties from KnockoutComputedDefine<T>
Append result types in DomData and DomNodeDisposal
Append method override for getFormFields with fieldName of type RegExp

Append types on memoization methods
Append selectExtensions
Append expressionRewriting
Append bindingProvider
Fix issues in KnockoutVirtualElements

Append missing methods to KnockoutUtils
- objectForEach
- peekObservable
- registerEventHandler
- compareArrays
- setDomNodeChildrenFromArrayMapping

Fix type issue in methods
- setHtml 
- unwrapObservable
- triggerEvent
- toggleDomNodeCssClass
- postJson
- strigifyJson
- applyBindings
- applyBindingsToDescendants
- applyBindingsToNode
- dataFor
- contextFor

Append top-level methods and fields :
- subscription
- dependentObservable
- unwrap ==> ko.utils.unwrapObservable
- isWriteableObservable

Fix issues in Templates :
Append specific interface for different TemplateEngine
Make template engines inherit from TemplateEngine
Append KnockouTemplateOptions interface

Recreate Template Source typing
Append KnockoutTemplateSource interface for inheritance
Append KnockoutTemplateSourceAnonymousTemplate type
Make KnockoutTemplateSourceDomElement inherits from KnockoutTemplateSource 

Simplify Static Interface by creating to generics types : 
- KnockoutPrototypeStatic
- KnockoutInstancePrototypeStatic
